  <steps>
    <step num="0">Preheat oven to 350°F (180˚C). </step>
    <step num="1">In a medium-sized mixing bowl, combine cheddar cheese, bacon, chives, salt, and pepper. </step>
    <step num="2">Spoon cheese mixture into a greased mini muffin tin. Press mixture into mini muffin tin. </step>
    <step num="3">Bake for 5-8 minutes or until cheese is melted and edges are slightly brown. </step>
    <step num="4">Cool on cooling rack or paper towel for 10 minutes. </step>
    <step num="5">Enjoy! </step>
  </steps>
